Name: ldap_member_method
Type: STRINGLIST
Allowed-Values: attribute filter
Default-Value: attribute
Last-Modified: 2.3.17

Specify a group method.

The *attribute* method retrieves groups from a multi-valued attribute
specified in :imapdconf:`ldap_member_attribute`.

The *filter* method uses a filter specified by
:imapdconf:`ldap_member_filter`.
